  "detailed_description": "In another failed invasion plan you were caught in a storm<br>Cut off contact with friends who have worked together for many years<br>The city was thrown into a mess by the explosion of the laboratory and the spread of the virus<br>You are blocked by many virus-infected creatures and enemies<br>You don’t know that you are the one who planned this conspiracy<br>The current game is already a reset version<br>Because the game is a work driven out by the author in advance<br>I haven’t finished the optimization yet. If the configuration is not high, friends can wait<br>I will update the game content and optimize patches<br>I wish you all a happy play!<br>(The author is still learning the knowledge of ue4 to makegames. I hope to be considerate of some technically immature places)<br>枪械射击<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/2edbdd7d071080c95f66aa57aa8e40ed.poster.avif?t=1772948511\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/2edbdd7d071080c95f66aa57aa8e40ed.webm?t=1772948511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/2edbdd7d071080c95f66aa57aa8e40ed.mp4?t=1772948511\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>怪物被攻击后收到的反应<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/e8eb2a5d5f4533975a48d53c47f0bb7e.poster.avif?t=1772948511\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/e8eb2a5d5f4533975a48d53c47f0bb7e.webm?t=1772948511\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1263220/extras/e8eb2a